                On our main stage we welcome live performances from THE HOOSIERS and ELIZA AND THE BEAR as well as a DJ set by PENDULUM ft Verse MC.Beside musical entertainment, we have the renowned magician Alan Hudson, who will be performing close up magic at our ball! Alan is an associate of the inner magic circle, London, has appeared on ITV’s hit Saturday night show Penn &amp; Teller: Fool Us with Jonathan Ross, BBC2’s Culture Show, ITV1’s Sooty Show, and BBC1’s The Holiday Show. Check out this video of Alan in action, prepare to be amazed! We will also be welcoming a trio of comedians including Joel Dommet, who many of you will know as DC Sweeney from Skins. He will be appearing as our headline comedy act along with Naz Osmanoglu and Ben Van Der Velde. There will be a fairground, a ceilidh, and many photo opportunities! If you need to refresh yourself or powder your nose, you will be able to make your way to our Powder Room where beauticians and masseuses will be on hand to help.
